Package GoNature

Class TotalVisitorsReport

  • java.lang.Object
    • GoNature.TotalVisitorsReport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class TotalVisitorsReport
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    TotalVisitorsReport represents a report containing information about total visitors to a park. It includes the number of visitors categorized by group visits, family visits, and individual visits, as well as the total number of visitors overall. Additionally, it provides arrays to store the number of visits for each day of the week. This class provides methods to retrieve and modify report details.
    Author:
    Pier Mbariky, Redan Ganim, Bassel Haddad, Joel Hourany, Asaad Sajim, Nadine Halabi
